Events.RelatedBody:
Repro steps:
1. Go to [API keys](https://dev.nugettest.org/account/ApiKeys) page as a collaborator on Microsoft org;
2. Switch owner to Microsoft org;
3. Notice that "Either a glob pattern must be specified or at least one package ID must be selected" validation error popped up under the "Select packages".
4. Notice no other validation errors;
5. Check and then uncheck "Push" checkbox;
6. Notice that there are two validation errors now (the new one is "At least one scope must be selected" under the "Select Scopes").

Validation error reporting should be consistent: either no, or both errors should show up.
